    <!-- About Section -->
    <section class="section" id="about">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">What is Biochemical Engineering?</h2>
            <div class="content-wrapper">
                <div class="text-content">
                    <p>Biochemical engineering integrates principles of biology, chemistry, and engineering to design processes that use living organisms or biological molecules to produce valuable products. This field bridges the gap between laboratory discoveries and industrial-scale applications, focusing on areas like pharmaceuticals, biofuels, and food production.</p>
                    <p>As a biochemical engineer, you'll work on developing and optimizing processes for producing antibiotics, vaccines, biofuels, and enzymes. You'll use techniques like fermentation, cell culture, and genetic engineering to create sustainable and efficient solutions for global challenges such as healthcare, energy, and environmental sustainability.</p>
                    <p>With the growing demand for biopharmaceuticals and renewable energy, biochemical engineering offers exciting career opportunities in industries that are shaping the future of science and technology.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Key Areas Section -->
    <section class="section bg-dark" id="key-areas">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">Key Areas of Study</h2>
            <p class="section-intro">Biochemical Engineering encompasses several specialized areas critical to advancing biotechnology and sustainable processes:</p>
            
            <div class="cards-grid three-columns">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h3><i class="fas fa-vial"></i> Fermentation Technology</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <p>Study of microbial and enzymatic processes to produce chemicals, fuels, and pharmaceuticals through controlled fermentation.</p>
                        <ul class="skills-list">
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Microbial Kinetics</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Growth models, substrate utilization</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Bioreactor Design</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Stirred tanks, air-lift reactors</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Scale-Up</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Lab to industrial-scale fermentation</p>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h3><i class="fas fa-dna"></i> Genetic Engineering</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <p>Manipulation of genetic material to enhance the production of proteins, enzymes, and other bio-products.</p>
                        <ul class="skills-list">
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Recombinant DNA</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Cloning, gene expression</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">CRISPR</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Gene editing techniques</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Synthetic Biology</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Designing biological systems</p>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h3><i class="fas fa-flask"></i> Bioprocess Engineering</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <p>Design and optimization of processes for large-scale production of biological products like vaccines and biofuels.</p>
                        <ul class="skills-list">
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Mass Transfer</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Oxygen transfer, mixing</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Process Control</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Automation, feedback systems</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Downstream Processing</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Purification, separation</p>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="cards-grid three-columns" style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h3><i class="fas fa-seedling"></i> Environmental Biotechnology</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <p>Use of biological processes to address environmental challenges like waste treatment and bioremediation.</p>
                        <ul class="skills-list">
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Bioremediation</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Degrading pollutants</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Wastewater Treatment</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Activated sludge, biofilters</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Bioenergy</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Biofuels, biogas production</p>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h3><i class="fas fa-prescription-bottle"></i> Biopharmaceuticals</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <p>Development of drugs and therapies using biological systems, including monoclonal antibodies and vaccines.</p>
                        <ul class="skills-list">
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Cell Culture</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Mammalian, microbial cultures</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Protein Engineering</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Antibody design, optimization</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">GMP Compliance</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Regulatory standards</p>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h3><i class="fas fa-microscope"></i> Enzyme Technology</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <p>Application of enzymes in industrial processes, including food, textiles, and pharmaceuticals.</p>
                        <ul class="skills-list">
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Enzyme Kinetics</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Reaction rates, inhibition</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Immobilization</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Enzyme stabilization</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Biocatalysis</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Enzyme-based reactions</p>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

